<h1 id="egyptian-randomness---algorithmic-composition">Egyptian Randomness - Algorithmic Composition</h1>

<p>In a <a href="https://www.kadenze.com/courses/introduction-to-programming-for-musicians-and-digital-artists/info"> MOOC taught by Ajay Kapur</a> I learned to program generative music using Chuck. Here are the results of my first project. A Random song using polyrythms based on the egyptian scale: C D Eb F# G Ab B C.</p>

