<h1 id="dream-fragmentation---audiovisual-experiment">Dream Fragmentation - Audiovisual Experiment</h1>

<p>Visuals generated transforming a Mandelbrot set with recursive zoom in Adobe After Effects and Max 7 Vizzie. Sounds synthesized with Arturia’s Modular V.</p>

